<td style="width:5em;">&#160;&#160;&#160;</td>
<td style="padding:0px;text-align:center;;;;width:16%;;">
<div>
<p><strong class="selflink">Lithium</strong><br />
<b><span class="chemf">Li</span></b><br />
<small>Atomic Number: 3<br />
Atomic Weight: 6.941<br />
Melting Point: 453.69<br />
Boiling Point: 1615<br />
Electronegativity: 0.98</small></p>
</div>
</td>
<td style="border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;padding:0px;text-align:center;;;;width:16%;;">
<div>
