</div>
</td>
<td style="border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;padding:0px;text-align:center;;;;width:16%;;">
<div>
<p><a href="/wiki/Potassium" title="Potassium">Potassium</a><br />
<b><span class="chemf">K</span></b><br />
<small>Atomic Number: 19<br />
Atomic Weight: 39.098<br />
Melting Point: 336.58<br />
Boiling Point: 1032<br />
Electronegativity: 0.82</small></p>
</div>
</td>
<td style="border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;padding:0px;text-align:center;;;;width:16%;;">
<div>
<p><a href="/wiki/Rubidium" title="Rubidium">Rubidium</a><br />
<b><span class="chemf">Rb</span></b><br />
<small>Atomic Number: 37<br />
Atomic Weight: 85.468<br />
Melting Point: 312.46<br />
Boiling Point: 961<br />
Electronegativity: 0.82</small></p>
</div>
</td>
<td style="border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;padding:0px;text-align:center;;;;width:16%;;">
<div>
<p><a href="/wiki/Caesium" title="Caesium">Caesium</a><br />
<b><span class="chemf">Cs</span></b><br />
<small>Atomic Number: 55<br />
Atomic Weight: 132.905<br />
Melting Point: 301.59<br />
Boiling Point: 944<br />
Electronegativity: 0.79</small></p>
</div>
</td>
<td style="border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;padding:0px;text-align:center;;;;width:16%;;">
<div>
<p><a href="/wiki/Francium" title="Francium">Francium</a><br />
